# dquants per-account deployment list  (template — copy to deployment_accounts.txt)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# One MT5 account per line, used by scripts/make_account_releases.sh to build
# one account-locked EA per line.
#
# Format:   <AccountID>  <ServerName>
#   - AccountID  : the MT5 login number (digits only)
#   - ServerName : the MT5 trade-server name exactly as shown in MT5
#                  (Tools > Options > Server, or the login dialog). Optional —
#                  leave it off to lock the login on ANY server. A login number
#                  is only unique within a server, so include it when you can.
#   - separator  : whitespace OR a comma. ServerName may contain spaces.
#   - blank lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored.
#
# The real file (deployment_accounts.txt) is gitignored — it holds live account
# numbers. You can also keep per-strategy lists that are auto-detected:
#   scripts/deployment_accounts.KK-KenKem.txt
#   scripts/deployment_accounts.KK-MasterVP.txt
#
# Examples:
12345678   FundedNext-Server
87654321   Exness-MT5Real8
22223333,  ICMarketsSC-MT5
11112222              # no server -> locks this login on any server
